499
00:37:57,442 --> 00:37:59,860
Abdullah, good to see you.

500
00:38:00,070 --> 00:38:01,153
TERRY:
Up.

501
00:38:01,947 --> 00:38:03,697
[ELEVATOR BELL DINGS]

