Thank you.

516
00:38:55,750 --> 00:38:58,293
My partners are the beneficiaries.

517
00:38:58,461 --> 00:39:00,838
To my partners, gentlemen.

518
00:39:02,966 --> 00:39:04,967
-Fitzgerald.
