with Priest.

526
00:39:31,995 --> 00:39:33,871
Let's get out of here.

527
00:39:36,249 --> 00:39:37,416
MAN 1:
Hey!

528
00:39:49,888 --> 00:39:51,430
You.

529
00:39:52,724 --> 00:39:54,933
