537
00:40:16,831 --> 00:40:18,290
MAN 3:
Ah!

538
00:40:22,545 --> 00:40:24,129
[CROWD GASP]

539
00:40:26,132 --> 00:40:27,549
I trusted you.

540
00:40:28,134 --> 00:40:30,552
-Jesus.
